  "description": "An American institution, Sloppy Joes are a family favourite across the States. They're called sloppy for a reason (so napkins at the ready!), and are made even more delicious by melty mozzarella. These sliders are great to tear and share, but keep your eyes peeled for anyone trying to steal one of yours!",
